{"tid":1783221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解會有人覺得體制內體制外兩條路係矛盾？","createTime":"2019-12-14T15:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T16:02:26.000Z","uid":205884,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c908f253c32b5951c05270c6016cb684d6b8db8b","tid":1783221,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"好多人覺得如果我地比力搞選舉<br />\n就係承認咗呢個不義既體制<br />\n而且真普選會變得不可能<br />\n<br />\n第一，好多分析都話<br />\n如果我地比力選，<span style=\"color: red;\">係好大機會贏</span><br />\n立會一過半，一唔批財政預算<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">成個政府就停擺</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問你仲點樣唔回應五大訴求？</span><br />\n而且立會主席有權調動議程<br />\n可以讓政府所有提案都無限期輪候<br />\n到時要議會抗爭既就係建制派<br />\n然後比保安抬走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而提名委員會過半，選出黃絲特首<br />\n全世界壓力底下中央無辦法唔委任<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地就可以自己搞政改<br />\n體制內改變體制</span><br />\n五部曲變翻三部曲烹走人大<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">通過就有真普選</span><br />\n<br />\n呢d好似天方夜譚，但唔係無可能<br />\n老蕭數到最好既情況下<br />\n我地<span style=\"color: gold;\">立會有四十席，提名委員會有647席</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要大家齊心，搞工會，註冊投票<br />\n每個人都肯做係必贏：<br />\n<br />\n史上最詳盡：普通人都加入到既功能組別名單，整理左好耐！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/apkoCQU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/apkoCQU</a><br />\n<br />\n第二，<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武之路代價極高，而成功無乜可能</span><br />\n首先你要知道，真正既對家係共產黨<br />\n特區政府只係共產黨隻狗<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">警隊更加只係共產黨隻狗既狗</span><br />\n而共產黨就算比你全城陷入火海<br />\n或者二百萬人以死相逼<br />\n都唔會動搖<br />\n喺呢d所謂革命論，所謂反抗體制既思想下<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">幾多手足為咗無望成功既目標<br />\n犧牲咗自己既前途甚至生命</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反，投票只是舉手之勞<br />\n註冊一下選民身份完全無阻平日抗爭<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">但大家都做成場運動就贏</span><br />\n<br />\n總之，翻翻去運動一開始時的精神<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武，和理非要唔割<br />\n但和理非出黎選，勇武都要去投<br />\n我們沒有分裂的本錢<br />\n可以走一步就走一步，盡做<br />\n咁樣我地最後一定會到煲底！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7df82a6e63000f1ddf5f51b467f25ca0d7a034","tid":1783221,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"612<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b810e5c5ca380a0c1c365ddf54438363341556a9","tid":1783221,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"895bc27a818b64a7cc3b2b8f150073fdff9c8013","tid":1783221,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:25:28.000Z","msg":"831<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c753294c3e4c914e28829858d9ca3caee036624","tid":1783221,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:25:49.000Z","msg":"101<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9a54a64c5599de1b7c4d90f1a921258ac6af1f","tid":1783221,"uid":221125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gpBRxin.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgpBRxin.jpg&h=2aefe025&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kohQNRJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkohQNRJ.jpg&h=4c3c97a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73f4a5309a3ef7affc8e3cbcbc28fe5eb1c3728d","tid":1783221,"uid":205884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:27:10.000Z","msg":"1021<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 